Uses of Package
org.cloudgraph.mapreduce

  • Packages that use org.cloudgraph.mapreduce 
    Package Description
    org.cloudgraph.hbase.mapreduce
    Contains MapReduce extension, implementation and other infrastructure classes which allow SDO data graphs of any depth or complexity, to be queried, consumed, produced and modified by Hadoop HBase MapReduce jobs.
    org.cloudgraph.hbase.service
    Contains HBase service provider implementation classes.
    org.cloudgraph.mapreduce  
    org.cloudgraph.rdb.service  
  • Classes in org.cloudgraph.mapreduce used by org.cloudgraph.hbase.mapreduce 
    Class and Description
    GraphAccessor
    Supports access to arbitrary data graphs at various stages of a Job as supplied based on the given query.
    GraphMutator
    Supports tracking and commit of modifications to arbitrary data graphs at various stages of a Job.
    GraphService
    Supports access, tracking and commit of modifications to arbitrary data graphs at various stages of a Job.
    GraphWritable
    Allows data graphs to be consumable by Hadoop using XML serialization under standard SDO provided mechanisms.
